{"type": "article", "id": 23379, "title": "hollis+morris 推出的极简抽象的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-07T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154029qaQL3rhRvNFZcV91.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是多伦多的设计工作室 hollis+morris 推出的家具系列，以木质家具为主。他们追求极简而抽象的审美，比如挂在墙上的灯就像一道闪电，而边桌则有近似三角形的支撑结构，也让桌子有了相应的朝向。而看似简单的椅子也有细小的转折结构，都流露出一种简单的优雅。<a href=\"http://www.hollismorris.com/\">这里是网站主页。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061540275h7T4w6VOgpnAfrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.61833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154027Xf9C16eOpLbAZQzj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154028bglzUCV2MNyuFsvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154028YFoTVPNBWrv27nhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154029RcjKnG7a1NAUOtZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}